# Bug Report #1 – Vehicle Clipping Through NPC

**Game:** GTA V  
**Platform:** PC  
**Type:** Physics Bug  
**Severity:** High  
**Status:** New  

## Description
When driving at high speed and colliding with an NPC at a specific angle, the NPC clips through the vehicle and disappears.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Drive at high speed in a crowded area
2. Hit an NPC from a side angle
3. Observe the NPC behavior

## Expected Result
NPC should collide and react physically (ragdoll)

## Actual Result
NPC clips through vehicle and disappears

## Frequency
3/10 times

## Notes
May be related to collision detection or physics engine timing



# Bug Report #2 – Ability Hitbox Inconsistency

**Game:** Valorant  
**Type:** Gameplay Bug  
**Severity:** Medium  

## Description
Certain abilities (e.g., molly-type) deal inconsistent damage near edges.

## Expected
Uniform damage within area of effect

## Actual
Edge zones sometimes deal no damage

## Impact
Affects competitive fairness
